channel.title: Computer can't portforward =[
channel.description:
When I portforward using my laptop's IP it works fine, the ports are open and all. But when I portforward using my hosting computer's IP the ports won't open at all for some reason and I do not understand why. So thinking it may be my router, I switch connections to my neighbor's which is very good connection and try to open a port and when I do, it still says the port is not open. So there is something wrong with my computer... Can anyone help me please?
If you can, add me on MSN :) klinker0319@hotmail.com
